@node Introduction "Introduction to EBP"

   EBP is a bible viewer utility designed for Workbench 2.0 and up.

Features include:

  - Single and multiple word searching.

  - Phrase searching.

  - Searching based on the matches of a previous search.

  - As many books can be opened as your memory will allow.

  - GUI Interface

  - Several screen modes are supported.

  - User bookmarks

  - The ability to save and recall search matches

@endnode

