@node Future "Future"

  Changes I'm thinking about making:

    - Multiple bibles available for different languages.

    - A lookup table for fast searching (This might be limited to the
      english version bible if it is ever implimented )

    - Arexx support (If I have enough requests for one )

    - Data compression ( XPK support ? )

    - Exporting verses to the Clipboard

@endnode

@node Tech "Tech"

Technical Details

  EBP has been developed and tested on:
    Modle: Amiga 1200 NTSC
    CPU:   68030 33MHz / 68882 33MHz

  The source:
    Compiler:      Amiga E v3.2e registered
                   68000 Assembly Code used for portions of the program
    Lines of Code: 1363
    Program Size:  70120

@endnode

@node History "History"

       V1.5
       *  Changed the progress meter.

       *  Added the ability to save/recall search matches.

       *  Added bookmark support

       *  Added a search feature allowing searching only the verses matched
          in the previous search.

       *  Added more screenmodes to the startup screen requester.

       *  EBP now goes to sleep while waiting for an input event,  in
          previous versions it would use some CPU time waiting on user input.

  2/98 V1.0
       *  Added the progress meter in the search command.

       *  Eliminated duplicate verse matches.

       *  Fixed phrase searching.

       *  Added (AND) and (OR) Searching.

       *  Added the screen requester on startup.

       *  Added limited ability to select the parts of the bible to
          search.

       *  Removed the console window and menus replacing them with a
          gadget window.

  1/98 V0.5Alpha  The first release

@endnode
